Organization = {Atypon; SHMAGH SOC; Green Circle; Inst Elect \& Elect Engineers},
Abstract = {The spread of smartphones with high quality digital cameras in
   combination with easy access to a myriad of software apps for recording,
   editing and sharing videos and digital images in combination with deep
   learning AI platforms has spawned a new phenomenon of faking videos
   known as Deepfake. We design and implement a deep-fake detection model
   with mouth features (DFT-MF), using deep learning approach to detect
   Deepfake videos by isolating, analyzing and verifying lip/ mouth
   movement. Experiments conducted against datasets that contain both fake
   and real videos showed favorable classification performance for DFT-MF
   model especially when compared with other work in this area.},
